- Parse index.html template for every request !
- Define a config file !
    - posts[
            {
                title: Main post title
                content:/path/to/md/file1,
                tags:["awesome-post", "what-post", "some-other-tag"],
                main:"my-first-post",
                author:"AkhlD",
                publish-date:"Day DD-Month-Year",
                seo-meta:"Random text to get it indexed"
            }
           ]
- Read config file for request !
- Match main or tag for request !
- Pull the content, attach it to the .content div
- Attach Author, publish date, seo-meta
- Respond

